# Summary
This documentation explains three methods for creating cohorts in Amplitude: using Microscope to create cohorts from data points (with limitations on when behavioral cohorts can be created), importing cohorts from CSV files containing user/group IDs, and creating inline behavioral/interval cohorts directly within the Segmentation module of most chart types.

